Reviews.original: The artwork effectively uses contrasting colors to enhance visual interest. The orange and yellow tones of the kennel and pillow contrast well with the black and white fur of the dog, making the dog stand out. The blue collar adds an additional pop of color that draws attention. However, the contrast could be more pronounced in some areas to create an even more striking visual impact.
